{"tid":1006532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宋有宋詞　粵有粵謳","createTime":"2019-02-03T05:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T06:11:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"41b6d2504f8edc0a3ecf1ea26b85f4bceccf03e8","tid":1006532,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bFzprSVfWMo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbFzprSVfWMo&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=c7cb61d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bFzprSVfWMo</a><br />\n<br />\n粵謳<br />\n<br />\n情唔好亂用，用錯就幾咁擔心。<br />\n人客總有箇多情，勸妹你慢慢嚟尋。<br />\n若然係亂咁鍾情，人哋就會拖妹你落氹。<br />\n條魚上釣，都因為猴擒。<br />\n大抵十箇男人，著九箇會噤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_PtkhTgujy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_PtkhTgujy0&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=db18671f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_PtkhTgujy0</a><br />\n<br />\n粵語詩<br />\n<br />\n荊軻嚇失佢三魂，好在良官冇扑親。<br />\n野仔執番條爛命，龜公害盡幾多人。<br />\n監生點解嚟陪葬，臨死唔知重拜神。<br />\n萬里咁長城一座，後來番鬼當新聞。"},{"pid":"0d0ca0fd4c0a44e6109f7b9ae13666c5777399bb","tid":1006532,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"粵文化真係博大精深！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ed47c7b825c472b589c9e22d93166a31b0888","tid":1006532,"uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"男極圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87bf83cc366e551fe23488746b6a93d1616d2ae","tid":1006532,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"每日150個腥港人，總有一日溝到得返好少人講粵語"},{"pid":"89887c28172bbdc18b0f18756ae522b0f2bd7269","tid":1006532,"uid":171107,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"所謂何東精神 就係團結<br />\n我地何東姊妹 自成一族<br />\n不但精明能幹 做野爽快<br />\n我地會煮糖水 又會煲粥<br />\n入左Kong u 就想住何東<br />\n入左何東就至醒目<br />\n問妹何所欲 問妹幾時申請入宿<br />\n問妹何所欲 問妹幾時新入宿」"},{"pid":"0842bc4684fadd14d37599a149ebea65e126aa0b","tid":1006532,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"粵謳、木魚書、南音，非常珍貴的粵文學材料費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d555a4afa1ee443c6e121da056102a082d37782","tid":1006532,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"我見妳婆婆好得喎 少女我唔鋤愛阿婆 <br />\n驅風煲老藕嗒得過 關節酸痛咪玩咁癲<br />\n七張幾處女啅得過"}]}